MBOMBELA – Anilda Groenewald, Hi-tech Nelspruit spokesman, said that they rushed to the incident just before you enter the Gorge. “The vehicle was on its way from Lydenburg toward Mozambique. The driver lost control of the vehicle and drove it into the bushes next to the road. Also read: Isis fighters infiltrate neighbouring Mozambique (Part 1) “The two men managed to escape with only minor injuries and Hi-tech took them to Rob Ferreira hospital to be treated,” Groenewald said. Traffic has not been affected by the accident.  